Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.21,0:00:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.09,0:00:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a silent night
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.76,0:00:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Eclipse was beginnin'
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.92,0:00:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasaneau setsuna o
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.88,0:00:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Kitto eien to shinjikomu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.26,0:00:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.84,0:01:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's darker than black
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.05,0:01:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Meikyuu no sora
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.51,0:01:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari o kou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.96,0:01:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If bite your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.76,0:01:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoudou ga mushibande yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.76,0:01:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I... Can I... Can I... Who am I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.30,0:01:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Risei o kakikesu libido
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.21,0:01:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,(Where is my heart?)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.38,0:01:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurayami ni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.67,0:01:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,(Where is my heart?)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.80,0:01:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ochikitta
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.01,0:01:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,(Where is my heart?)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.17,0:01:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Minikui sugata ni natte
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.76,0:01:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hito no namida kareta nara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.17,0:01:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimi wa boku o dou omou no ka?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.13,0:01:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotae o oshiete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.05,0:01:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Makka na chi ga
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.96,0:01:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,(Bloody bonds)\NMakka na chi ga
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.13,0:01:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kizuna o nurashiai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.21,0:01:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yowasa o wakeatte
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.80,0:01:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,(Bloody bonds)\NYowasa o wakeatte
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.92,0:01:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Futari wa ikite yuku no ka?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.34,0:01:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kizu o nameatte
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:01:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sei o teigi shiatte
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:02:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai o musabotte
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.05,0:02:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an3}Safe House
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.30,0:02:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.34,0:02:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How about Taira?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.71,0:02:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.76,0:02:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.13,0:02:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You alive, Taira?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.96,0:02:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You can stay in your seat,\Nbut would you read paragraph three?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.51,0:02:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Page 136 of the text.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.59,0:02:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.92,0:02:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Medieval communes in the European Middle Ages\Nhad sworn allegiances of mutual defense...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.17,0:02:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Medieval communes in the European Middle Ages\Nhad sworn allegiances of mutual defense...\NIt's been one month since Akimura disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.88,0:02:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been one month since Akimura disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.30,0:02:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They're saying he's studying abroad in Canada.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.51,0:02:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,His arrest wasn't on the news.\NIs that because he was a vampire?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen Anzai once since the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What if...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.59,0:02:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I imagined the whole thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.13,0:03:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.26,0:03:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Um! There's a syringe sticking out of your leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.84,0:03:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I did it on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.67,0:03:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I'm using a sedative on myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.13,0:03:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do my eyes look normal now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.13,0:03:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? He looks so much better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.59,0:03:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The dark circles are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.17,0:03:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.42,0:03:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that. With the tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.71,0:03:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to remind me there was tongue!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.13,0:03:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I said sorry! Don't hit me! Stop it!\NYou don't have to remind me there was tongue!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.38,0:03:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I said sorry! Don't hit me! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.38,0:03:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.88,0:03:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a vampire, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.46,0:03:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.21,0:03:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Oh, no, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.42,0:03:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I have genes from both,\Nso I guess I'm a half vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.51,0:03:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Half...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:03:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was under the impression\Nmy bloodlust was weaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But apparently not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All of Akimura's self-control, and I almost wasted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.55,0:04:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, cheer up, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.05,0:04:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.63,0:04:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There are plenty of fish in the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.13,0:04:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.30,0:04:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Since then, I haven't seen Anzai once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.05,0:04:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because he kissed me?\NIs that why I can't stop thinking about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.59,0:04:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that's not how real love is supposed to work, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.38,0:04:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Akimura?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.26,0:05:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you're okay, Akimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.46,0:05:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.34,0:05:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,have I ever really fallen in love with anyone before?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.67,0:05:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, that was basically my first kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where you are now, Anzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't scare me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.96,0:05:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.96,0:05:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Anzai?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.34,0:05:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-why are you on my balcony?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.46,0:05:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I came via telephone pole.\NIt was the closest entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.09,0:05:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Telephone pole?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.21,0:05:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.76,0:05:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.51,0:05:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're worried about Akimura, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You always stop for a minute when you\Nget to the place we arrested him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.34,0:05:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can put in a request for you if you want to visit him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:06:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And depending on the trial,\Nsometimes they get off with just a life sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a terrible person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so busy thinking about Anzai,\NI forgot about Akimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.42,0:06:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.05,0:06:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you gotten skinnier?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.13,0:06:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You know guys prefer a girl with\Na little meat on her bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow! Don't punch me! Not the fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.17,0:06:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.26,0:06:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing much better than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.42,0:06:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He... he smiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.34,0:06:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawazaki here. We have a Level 1 Special Case!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Our suspect is Yuuko Tamaru, age 21. Female.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.09,0:06:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hereafter the investigation will\Nrefer to her as Target T.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We believe she is currently\Nhiding out in the Mikusa Building.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.21,0:06:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Anzai. I copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm close. I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.67,0:07:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Mikusa Building
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.51,0:07:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to settle this peacefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.63,0:07:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuko Tamaru, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The police?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.51,0:07:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Public Security Division 5, for devil-related crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We can make special allowances in cases like yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no priors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.71,0:07:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If you claim it was an accident,\Nthey might not press charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.05,0:07:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Charges?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.46,0:07:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care what they do to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.76,0:07:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why are you running, Yuuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.30,0:07:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.13,0:07:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.09,0:07:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone you'd do anything to protect?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't, you wouldn't understand how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.55,0:07:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He meant the world to me.\NHe was helping me make dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.71,0:08:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He slipped and cut his finger. Then he said...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"Lick it off?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The next thing I knew, I had stabbed him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and I had been desperately drinking his blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.92,0:08:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.42,0:08:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I was always so careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.59,0:08:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So careful not to hurt him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.59,0:08:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have known it wouldn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.30,0:08:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A devil marrying a human...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.46,0:08:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Living under the same roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.67,0:08:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn right it didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.71,0:08:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He stuck out his bloody finger\Nand asked you to lick it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.67,0:08:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What part of that is "being careful"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.34,0:08:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if he was your husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.30,0:08:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If you see blood, you're gonna lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.34,0:08:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So I guess you didn't really teach your husband\Nhow scary devils can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.05,0:08:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you'd do anything to protect him,\Nbut you were just afraid he'd stop liking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't leave out the important stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.51,0:09:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,December 3, 23:35.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.71,0:09:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Target T was arrested on charges of\Nassault by F Squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.51,0:09:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Present on the scene: Senior Officer Sawazaki
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.51,0:09:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and Officer Anzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.71,0:09:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You followed me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.17,0:09:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And hello? You didn't even lock the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.76,0:09:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A woman alone, in the middle of the night!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.96,0:09:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes. You're right, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.38,0:09:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But you left this here, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.42,0:10:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised he's actually apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.38,0:10:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But from now on,\Nyou don't have to bring me my stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.01,0:10:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.17,0:10:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... that woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,An old friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.92,0:10:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We made snowmen together when we were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.96,0:10:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.46,0:10:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you ever get hurt in front of me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.71,0:10:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not easy to arrange for\Nnon-family members to visit a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.76,0:10:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But they might make an exception if the visitor\Ncould help the devil reform himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to see him, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.30,0:10:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:11:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, um... if you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A kotatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.09,0:11:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have one?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.84,0:11:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I only have the things I need to get by.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.05,0:11:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I think everyone needs one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.84,0:11:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you get cold easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.34,0:11:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but my temperature's usually about 80 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.38,0:11:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-that's low!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.51,0:11:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Anzai. Where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.59,0:11:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times have I told you\Nto stop running off on your-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.59,0:11:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And you make sure to lock your door.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.21,0:11:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.80,0:11:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Do it with somebody watching? Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.38,0:11:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.34,0:11:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Anzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, here are your sedatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.34,0:11:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks. This'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.71,0:11:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Sawazaki? Not here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.84,0:11:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.42,0:11:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he's gonna be lecturing you all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.71,0:11:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Something about you running off on your own again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.13,0:11:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:11:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been such a stranger lately, Yuuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.46,0:12:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,When you have this wonderful older woman taking\Npity on you and inviting you over for some company.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.51,0:12:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Water, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.71,0:12:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Are you two dating?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.21,0:12:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please. Of course we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.05,0:12:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.01,0:12:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,"Of course we are" not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.84,0:12:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.51,0:12:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't believe her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So? What were you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.92,0:12:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Just about a ridiculous new clause\Nthey added to the guidelines.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.38,0:12:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Devil Conduct Guidelines Article 1:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.59,0:12:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sexual intercourse between a human\Nand a vampire will now be legal,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,as long as there is consent from\Nboth parties and a doctor is present.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.17,0:12:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But is that really a good idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.09,0:12:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That "Tamaru" couple, they were a human and a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.05,0:12:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They even signed a prenup promising not to\Nhave sex, and look how that turned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of hot pot should I make?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.63,0:13:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Hot pot?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.76,0:13:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,In your apartment?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cold out on the balcony.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.30,0:13:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was hoping we could talk more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.21,0:13:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait. That's no reason to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.84,0:13:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't just go in your room. That would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.13,0:13:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If... if it can...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.67,0:13:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,wait until after my squad meeting tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.55,0:13:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll stop by the store on my way\Nhome from class and buy ingredients.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything you-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you so happy about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What? N-nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.96,0:13:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, if you wait until my meeting's over,\Nwe can meet up and I can carry the bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.01,0:13:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what school do you go to again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.46,0:14:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, Professor Ochiai's office is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.17,0:14:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.63,0:14:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The lights are on-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.88,0:14:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Taira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.34,0:14:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You startled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.84,0:14:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.55,0:14:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I came to return the book I borrowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What? So YOU had it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.88,0:14:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,S-sorry. I kept forgetting to return it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.92,0:14:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Is it snowing outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.13,0:14:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. You must be cold, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.01,0:14:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you stay and warm up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.51,0:14:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,N-no, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.17,0:14:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can at least make you some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.59,0:14:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Devils and humans should\Nlive apart from each other, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.88,0:14:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did that come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.51,0:14:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Not from me. It's Anzai's creed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.17,0:15:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently Target T, Yuuko Tamaru, lived at\Nthe orphanage with him when they were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.26,0:15:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess he's had a lot to think about\Nafter we arrested that serial killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.71,0:15:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been checking on the girl who was\Nthe motive behind the murders ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.42,0:15:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. Careful, it's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.42,0:15:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.84,0:15:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So, ummm... Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.01,0:15:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.09,0:15:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm just being neurotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.59,0:15:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Something about him scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.17,0:15:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.26,0:15:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I was scared the other day when he...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.01,0:15:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But wait... he was a total stranger, kissing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, that would be much worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.67,0:15:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Something is wrong with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.84,0:15:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Your timing was perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.76,0:15:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I got another good book.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.59,0:15:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking I'd lend it to you next time I saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I just had one of your books for over six months.\NI couldn't borrow another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:15:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, as long as it leads to a good thesis, I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.51,0:16:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You can keep this one another six months if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.26,0:16:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.09,0:16:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, if you really don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.42,0:16:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not expect to be out this late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.34,0:16:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a good place to wait?\NThat guy's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.05,0:16:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Think he's waiting for somebody?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.71,0:16:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh! He'll hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.17,0:16:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm just asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.59,0:16:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I doing?\NWell, I'm just asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,N-no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.38,0:16:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so like you, not to swing it\Nstraight at me, Taira.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.09,0:16:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But I really liked that mug.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.76,0:16:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.92,0:17:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.84,0:17:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.92,0:17:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't have to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If you didn't want me to,\Nyou could have just said so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.63,0:17:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,J-just said so...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But even if I don't, that doesn't mean you can just...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.21,0:17:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I thought silence was consent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Professor... You're married.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.51,0:17:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You have children...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.92,0:17:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your point?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, in the end, whether or not someone\Nturns into a monster is entirely up to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.42,0:17:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.84,0:18:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.05,0:18:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.42,0:18:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,S-stop! That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.42,0:18:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.76,0:18:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Ochiai?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.09,0:18:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that sound? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.05,0:18:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Call the police.\NYou can just tell them a vampire got in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.01,0:18:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And tell them about the sexual assault\Nwhen they get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.67,0:18:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you have a spare key?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.67,0:19:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.42,0:19:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.09,0:19:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Ochiai! Are you okay? What's wrong?\NWh-what happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Ochiai! Are you okay? What's wrong?\NCall an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How in the world did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Wait! Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.63,0:19:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be disciplined for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.88,0:19:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is her blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.92,0:19:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to wash it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.96,0:19:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.59,0:19:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Ochiai was given a disciplinary dismissal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}NOTICE\N{\an5}Professor of Humanities\N{\an5}Keiji Ochiai\N{\an5}The above professor has been found in
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.43,0:19:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}serious breach of school policy.\N{\an5}He has been dismissed accordingly.\N{\an5}Keio University Dean
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.21,0:19:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My hand has healed up, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.38,0:20:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.51,0:20:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But since that night...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.13,0:20:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been seeing Professor Ochiai in my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.26,0:20:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.01,0:20:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what he's doing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.05,0:20:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha... you're awake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.71,0:20:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.92,0:20:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, um. That's to thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.55,0:20:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You made this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.17,0:20:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.21,0:21:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.01,0:21:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. Are you afraid of men?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.55,0:21:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not scared. Not of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.71,0:21:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you scared of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.88,0:21:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.01,0:21:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Your jacket is pretty warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.05,0:21:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I wear it, I feel like I won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.09,0:21:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,have so many bad dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.71,0:21:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're having nightmares?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.30,0:21:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you something, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.55,0:21:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A present.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.13,0:22:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sotto tokete yuku you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Motto ai shiaetara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.01,0:22:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Nani o tsutaerareta no
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.09,0:22:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai o tsumugenai meguriawase
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.55,0:22:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Dare ka yurushite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.76,0:22:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Kegareta sugata ga boku de aru koto o
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.51,0:22:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Aa doushite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.76,0:22:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Fureru yubi ga furueteiru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.34,0:22:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's story of fight together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.55,0:22:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Dakishimetai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.80,0:22:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Kizu tsukezu ni mamoritai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.51,0:22:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Anata dake o
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.76,0:22:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's story of desire forever
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.34,0:23:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Aragai tsuzukeru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.92,0:23:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wakiagaru shoudou ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.51,0:23:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"Aa, mata boku wa..."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.01,0:23:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Deep red dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.59,0:23:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sotto futari tokete yuku you ni...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.09,0:23:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Next Time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.63,0:23:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Devils' Line:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.63,0:23:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Line 3,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.51,0:23:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,"Paradox."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.05,0:23:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Paradox